&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About other options:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bilhana:&lt;/strong&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;He was a&amp;nbsp;Sanskrit writer and a well-known Kashmiri poet.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;He was born in &lt;strong&gt;Kavi Bilhana&lt;/strong&gt; in the middle of the 11th century.&lt;/li&gt;
